## Key API Endpoints

| Endpoint | Purpose |
| -------- | ------- |
| `POST /api/auth/signup` | User registration |
| `POST /api/auth/login` | JWT login |
| `POST /api/parse-resume` | Resume upload + ATS analysis |
| `POST /api/transcribe` | Audio → text (`gpt-4o-transcribe`) |
| `POST /api/interview/session/create` | Create interview session |
| `POST /api/interview/start-with-audio` | Start session, get first question + audio |
| `POST /api/interview/submit-answer-realtime` | Submit answer, get AI response + next question |
| `POST /api/interview/submit-followup` | Handle follow-up elaborations |
| `GET /api/interview/conversation-state/{session_id}` | Debug: full context |
| `GET /api/audio/{filename}` | Serve cached MP3 files |
| `POST /api/tts/generate` | On-demand TTS generation |
| `POST /api/tts/batch` | Batch TTS generation |
| `POST /api/interview/start-with-job-description` | Start with JD intro (Phase 1D) |
| `POST /api/interview/rephrase-question` | LLM rephrase + TTS on silence timeout |
| `POST /api/job-description/parse` | Parse uploaded JD |

> **Arena TTS:** Questions, motivation, rephrase, presence warnings, and wrap-up use `playInterviewerSpeech()` → `/api/tts/generate`. SpeechSynthesis is fallback only.

## Decision Engine Priority

1. Challenge contradiction (Q≥5, confidence>0.7)
2. Deep dive (topic mentioned 3+ times, Q≥4)
3. Follow-up probe (vague/incomplete answer)
4. Reference past answer (similarity>0.85)
5. Standard next question (default)

