## Local Dev

```bash
# Backend (requires DATABASE_URL in backend/.env)
cd backend
pip install -r requirements.txt
uvicorn api:app --reload

# Frontend (from repo root — NOT frontend/)
npm install
npm run dev
# → http://localhost:5173
```

